last_episode_to_air.name: A Hogg in the Foggy Bog
last_episode_to_air.overview: Jesse finds Cyrus Duke's treasure map and meets up with Bo, Luke and Daisy in the Phillippines to find it. They are going to turn in the $20 million so they can get the reward and pay off the mortgage. Unfortunately, the Dukes are going to have to outmaneuver Boss and a crook named Richards, who are after the treasure for themselves.

name: The Dukes
overview: The Dukes is an animated series which ran on CBS in 1983 based directly on the popular live-action television series The Dukes of Hazzard.
